BlackBox.name: DVI.ecp5pll25To250
BlackBox.template:
(* FREQUENCY_PIN_CLKI="25" *)
(* FREQUENCY_PIN_CLKOP="250" *)
(* ICP_CURRENT="12" *) (* LPF_RESISTOR="8" *) (* MFG_ENABLE_FILTEROPAMP="1" *) (* MFG_GMCREF_SEL="2" *)
EHXPLLL #(
        .PLLRST_ENA("DISABLED"),
        .INTFB_WAKE("DISABLED"),
        .STDBY_ENABLE("DISABLED"),
        .DPHASE_SOURCE("DISABLED"),
        .OUTDIVIDER_MUXA("DIVA"),
        .OUTDIVIDER_MUXB("DIVB"),
        .OUTDIVIDER_MUXC("DIVC"),
        .OUTDIVIDER_MUXD("DIVD"),
        .CLKI_DIV(1),
        .CLKOP_ENABLE("ENABLED"),
        .CLKOP_DIV(2),
        .CLKOP_CPHASE(0),
        .CLKOP_FPHASE(0),
        .FEEDBK_PATH("CLKOP"),
        .CLKFB_DIV(10)
    ) ~NAME[0] (
        .RST(1'b0),
        .STDBY(1'b0),
        .CLKI(~ARG[1]),
        .CLKOP(~RESULT[1]), // clkout0 output
        .CLKFB(~RESULT[1]), // clkout0 output
        .CLKINTFB(),
        .PHASESEL0(1'b0),
        .PHASESEL1(1'b0),
        .PHASEDIR(1'b1),
        .PHASESTEP(1'b1),
        .PHASELOADREG(1'b1),
        .PLLWAKESYNC(1'b0),
        .ENCLKOP(1'b0),
        .LOCK(~RESULT[0]) // locked output
);
